OL,5,EWILL I MAKE A FOOL OF MYSELF?Wvs|||a}2
OL,6,                                    W*%
OL,7, Nick replies                           
OL,8, BJust because this guy has moved       
OL,9, Bdoesn't mean you can't get to know him
OL,11, BYour idea of banging on his door and  
OL,12, Basking him out is simple. It's not    
OL,13, Blike you're a stranger. He might like 
OL,14, Bthe company but don't get too heavy.  
OL,16,BBWith him in the next town it might    
OL,17,B spur you into action rather than      
OL,18, Bwaiting for something accidental      
OL,19, Bto happen.                            
